quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,7,"inn mushriqeen ke liye Allah aur is ke rasool ke nazdeek koi ehad aakhir kaisay ho sakta hai? bajuz unn logon ke jin se tum ne masjid haraam ke paas moahida kya tha, to jab taq woh tumahray sath seedhay rahen tum bhi un ke sath seedhay raho kyunkay Allah Muttaqiyun ko pasand karta hai"
9,8,magar inn ke siwa dosray mushriqeen ke sath koi ehad kaisay ho sakta hai jabkay unn ka haal yeh hai ke tum par qaboo pa jayen to nah tumahray maamla mein kisi qaraabat ka lehaaz karen nah kisi moahida ki zimma daari ka woh apni zabanon se tum ko raazi karne ki koshish karte hain magar dil un ke inkaar karte hain aur un mein se aksar fasik hain
9,9,unhon ne Allah ki ayaat ke badlay thori si qeemat qubool kar li phir Allah ke rastay mein sadday-rah (rokawat) ban kar kharray ho gay bohat buray kartoot thay jo yeh karte rahay
9,10,kisi momin ke maamla mein nah yeh qaraabat ka lehaaz karte hain aur nah kisi ehad ki zimma daari ka aur zayad-ti hamesha unhi ki taraf se hui hai
9,11,pas agar yeh tauba kar len aur namaz qaim karen aur zkoh den to tumahray dainee bhai hain aur jan-nay walon ke liye hum apne ehkaam wazeh kiye dete hain
9,12,aur agar ehad karne ke baad yeh phir apni qasmon ko toar dalain aur tumahray deen par hamlay karne shuru kar den to kufar ke almbrdaron se jung karo kyunkay un ki qasmon ka aitbaar nahi shayad ke ( phir talwar hi ke zor se ) woh baz ayen ge
9,13,kya tum nah lrho ge aisay logon se jo apne ehad torte rahay hain aur jinhon ne rasool ko malik se nikaal dainay ka qasad kya tha aur zayad-ti ki ibtida karne walay wohi thay? kya tum un se drtay ho? agar tum momin ho to Allah iss ka ziyada mustahiq hai ke is se daro
